How to run the program
----------------------

-> run make command to compile 
-> run make run command to execute the program
(you can change exit(1)->exit(0) in testcases.c files so that it can run all testcase without any error )

References:
-----------
-> https://www.cse.iitb.ac.in/~mythili/teaching/cs744_autumn2017/references/LittleBookOfSemaphores.pdf
